      "lines": [
        "AP 关注的是精确率-召回率的关系。",
        "但有时我们需要关注另一种关系：假正率和真正率。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s044",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "假正率（FPR）表示负类样本中被误判的比例。",
        "真正率（TPR）就是召回率。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answers": [
          "0.2",
          "0.6"
        ],
        "explanation": "阈值0.85时，FP=1, TN=4, FPR=1/5=0.2, TP=3, FN=2, TPR=3/5=0.6。",
        "kind": "fill_in_blank",
        "prompt": "当阈值设为 0.85 时，FPR 和 TPR 分别是多少？"
      },
      "focus_terms": [],
      "id": "s045",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "假设有10个样本，分数从高到低为：",
        "0.95(+), 0.93(+), 0.87(-), 0.85(+), 0.85(-), 0.85(-), 0.76(-), 0.53(+), 0.43(-), 0.25(+)。",
        "计算阈值=0.85 时的 FPR 和 TPR。"
      ],
      "type": "exercise"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "roc_curve"
      ],
      "id": "s046",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "roc_curve"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "把每个阈值下的 (FPR, TPR) 点连起来，",
        "就得到了 <term id=\"roc_curve\">ROC 曲线</term>。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "false_positive_rate",
        "true_positive_rate"
      ],
      "id": "s047",
      "introduced_terms": [
        "false_positive_rate",
        "true_positive_rate"
      ],
      "lines": [
        "ROC 曲线的横轴是 <term id=\"false_positive_rate\">假正率</term>（FPR），",
        "纵轴是 <term id=\"true_positive_rate\">真正率</term>（TPR）。"
      ],
      "type": "narration"
    },
    {
      "focus_terms": [
        "false_positive_rate",
        "true_positive_rate"
      ],
      "formula": {
        "latex": "\\text{FPR} = \\frac{FP}{FP + TN}",
        "spoken": "假正率等于 FP 除以 FP 加 TN。"
      },
      "id": "s048",
      "introduced_terms": [],
      "lines": [
        "FPR 表示负类样本中被误判的比例。",
        "我们希望 FPR 尽量低，TPR 尽量高。"
      ],
      "type": "formula"
    },
    {
      "exercise": {
        "answers": [
          "0.0,0.2",
